      "para_id": "Q001751.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Nuska , the chancellor of Enlil , his master , Ur-Nanibgal , governor of Nibru , child of Lugal-engardug , governor of Nibru , dedicated this ( seal ) for the well-being of Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad ."
    }
  ],
